  "subject": "[COMMON] Update mariadb template to use proper credentials",
  "commit_message": "[COMMON] Update mariadb template to use proper credentials\n\nDue to the fact that user DB credentials are created using mariadb-init\nproject according to (userCredentialsExternalSecret) and it is the same\nfor both shared db and local instance, it is needed to solve how\ntemplate retrieve user credentials to access the used db in template:\n(common.mariadbSecret) defined under (_mariadb.tpl) in\ncommon\\common\\templates\n\nIssue-ID: OOM-2819\nSigned-off-by: Mahmoud Abdelhamid <mahmoud.abdelhamid@orange.com>\nChange-Id: I1a37a30a794da06addf7e8498fa5b08ce8c3b2b5\n",
